---
title: Caribbean Lentil & Veggie Pie with Coconut Kumara Mash Topping
description: And now for something completely different, meet our game-changing veggie pie. With lentils cooked in a creamy coconut sauce
flavoured with Caribbean spices, plus a kumara mash topping, it ticks all the boxes while being nourishing and delicious.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/caribbean-lentil-veggie-pie-b9c4e52b.jpg
